modShortDescription: Adds a unbreakable and paintable block helper, a indestructible landmine, a few indestructible doors, powered doors and lights.
modDescription:
Adds a unbreakable and paintable block helper, a indestructible landmine, a few indestructible doors, powered doors and [lights](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-lights/).

Adds all the rotations to the garage doors and adds an item that gives 10000 xP. Also fixes the vehicle and apparel stacknumber to 1 to fix problems with other mods, specially the ones the add new dyes.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Snufki-n/Snufkin_Modlets/tree/master/Snufkin_AdminBlocksAndFixes)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/18673-snufkins-assorted-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Snufkin](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/snufkin/)
